# Security Model

## Roles

### user
- Create requests
- Read/edit own records only
- Cannot delete
- Cannot see SSN field

### agent
- Read/write all records
- Cannot see SSN field
- Cannot delete

### admin
- Full access
- Can view SSN field
- Can delete records

---

## Record-Level Enforcement

Table ACL script ensures:
- HR agents/admins → full visibility
- Users → only own records

---

## Field-Level Enforcement

Field ACL on:
u_ssn_last4

Only role:
x_<scope>_hr_sec_lite.admin
